summary: Adds a freeplay command to the console that skips to alduien\'s bane quest gives you good stats
descriptionHtml:
What this mod aims to do is for those who get bored of the main campain and just what to explore  the mod adds a freeplay command to the console that sets all stats to 75 and completes main storyline.

#################
Still in beta so Buggy#
#################

############# Install #############   
Place MQC.txt into your skyrim folder (Not Data Folder!)  
C:\\Program Files (x86)\\Steam\\steamapps\\(username)\\Skyrim
############ Use ###############
Type \"bat MQC\" in console
{Must have escaped Helgen!!!} 
########### Changelog ##########
2.7
Made it so you only level to 5 instead of 30
